List of Common Clusters Example

ex.common.clusters.Rd

Clusters that contain PTMs that are found to cocluster in all 3 T-SNE lists.

Usage

ex.common.clusters

Format

List of 40 lists:

list

Common cluster between the three distance metrics

Source

"Created in MakeCorrelationNetwork, FindCommonClusters using 3 T-SNE lists"

Examples
